A FRIENDLY REBUKE TO ONE Par&s;on <HI>BENJAMIN;</HI> Particularly relating to his Quarrelling with his Own CHURCH, and Vin|dicating the <HI>DISSENTERS.</HI></P>
<P><HI>By One of the People called</HI> QUAKERS.</P>
